fields.name: ApiId
fields.description: API identifier path. /apis/{apiId}

fields.name: ApiRegion
fields.description: API region identifier.

fields.name: ApiTimeAvg
fields.description: Average time it took to process request.

fields.name: ApiTimeMax
fields.description: Maximum time it took to process request.

fields.name: ApiTimeMin
fields.description: Minimum time it took to process request.

fields.name: Bandwidth
fields.description: Bandwidth consumed.

fields.name: CacheHitCount
fields.description: Number of times when content was served from cache policy.

fields.name: CacheMissCount
fields.description: Number of times content was fetched from backend.

fields.name: CallCountBlocked
fields.description: Number of calls blocked due to invalid credentials. This includes calls returning HttpStatusCode.Unauthorized and HttpStatusCode.Forbidden and HttpStatusCode.TooManyRequests

fields.name: CallCountFailed
fields.description: Number of calls failed due to proxy or backend errors. This includes calls returning HttpStatusCode.BadRequest(400) and any Code between HttpStatusCode.InternalServerError (500) and 600

fields.name: CallCountOther
fields.description: Number of other calls.

fields.name: CallCountSuccess
fields.description: Number of successful calls. This includes calls returning HttpStatusCode <= 301 and HttpStatusCode.NotModified and HttpStatusCode.TemporaryRedirect

fields.name: CallCountTotal
fields.description: Total number of calls.

fields.name: Country
fields.description: Country to which this record data is related.

fields.name: Interval
fields.description: Length of aggregation period.  Interval must be multiple of 15 minutes and may not be zero. The value should be in ISO 8601 format (http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ISO_8601#Durations).

fields.name: Name
fields.description: Name depending on report endpoint specifies product, API, operation or developer name.

fields.name: OperationId
fields.description: Operation identifier path. /apis/{apiId}/operations/{operationId}

fields.name: ProductId
fields.description: Product identifier path. /products/{productId}

fields.name: Region
fields.description: Country region to which this record data is related.

fields.name: ServiceTimeAvg
fields.description: Average time it took to process request on backend.

fields.name: ServiceTimeMax
fields.description: Maximum time it took to process request on backend.

fields.name: ServiceTimeMin
fields.description: Minimum time it took to process request on backend.

fields.name: SubscriptionId
fields.description: Subscription identifier path. /subscriptions/{subscriptionId}

fields.name: Timestamp
fields.description: Start of aggregation period. The date conforms to the following format: `yyyy-MM-ddTHH:mm:ssZ` as specified by the ISO 8601 standard.

fields.name: UserId
fields.description: User identifier path. /users/{userId}

fields.name: Zip
fields.description: Zip code to which this record data is related.
